mplementing distributed ledger technology as a secure and transparent way to digitally track the ownership of assets several different privateclosedloop versions are therefore already in existence as well as original distributed ones such as ours who are we what do we do nxchain is a us public company quoted on the otcmarkets in new york with the ticker code otcqbnxcn we’re a digital payments platform connecting digital currencies and fiat money currently moving into adjacent sectors within payments pos transactions and remittance our longterm target is to create a fully liquid digital payments system for global use nxchain is operated by a team of payment industry professionals who have been working on blockchain projects since  we have created a broad digital payments platform including free smartphone bankingpayments apps pilots released q  public release q  free smsbased bankingpayments apps in testing payment gateway accepting credit cards released q  online micropayment tools pilots released q  public release q  online merchant platforms in pilot testing going into production q  microlending platform incomplete pilots planned for q  open api for integrating any related service released in pilot testing platformspecific payment backbones pending release with third parties land registry blockchaintoken systems the nxchain platform is a payment transaction services suite combining a wide range of services from free secure mobile accounts to advanced industrial payment services we aim for recreating the financial environment presently covered by fiat currency in several markets and niches by offering a single stable transaction backbone tailored for quick instantsettlement payments with no minimum limits our initial product range was released on october st  including a digitalfiat currency payment gateway and a hybrid banking service the product suite will be added to and improved on a regular basis including proprietary platforms and ma incorporated services nxchain inc  mitchell north irvine california  infonxchaincom follow usnewsletter shortcutshome news business areas investor relations about us contact scroll to top nxcn key statistics  nxchain inc financial ratios  marketwatch bulletin investor alert new york markets close in market snapshot winners and losers expand keep open close expand keep open close expand keep open close expand keep open close expand keep open close nxchain inc otc nxcn go set alerts find a broker join td ameritrade market index overview profile news charts financials historical quotes analyst estimates options sec filings insiders marketstatecountryus nxchain inc market open  quotes are delayed by  min jun    pm nxcn quoteszigmandelayed   change   volume volume  quotes are delayed by  min quoteszigmandelayed previous close     change   day low day high na na  week low  week high   company description nxchain inc develops and implements advanced warehouse management software solutions it provides supply chain execution software solutions hardware implementation and training services as well as help desk support to its customers the company was founded in june  and is headquartered in tu nxchain inc develops and implements advanced warehouse management software solutions it provides supply chain execution software solutions hardware implementation and training services as well as help desk support to its customers the company was founded in june  and is headquartered in tustin ca valuation pe current  pe ratio with extraordinary items  enterprise value to ebitda  total debt to enterprise value  efficiency liquidity current ratio  quick ratio  cash ratio  profitability capital structure total debt to total capital  total debt to total assets  officers and executives name age officer since title mr sean tabatabai   president ceo secretary treasurer  director insider actions – purchase – sale  – number of transactions for more information visit the ft lexiconlexicon on this pageexplore our toolsale